PN,40201
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1775754356
OL,3,CAlbert Bridge now closed to all
OL,4,Ctraffic, walkers and cyclists
OL,6,FNo one can walk or cycle over Albert
OL,7,FBridge until further notice after a
OL,8,Fcrack was found in a key part of the
OL,9,Fstructure.
OL,11,FThe bridge was already closed to
OL,12,Ftraffic after engineers examined the
OL,13,F153 year old Grade II listed structure.
OL,15,FKensington and Chelsea Council said
OL,16,Fthe crossing was shut as a precaution
OL,17,Fafter sensors picked up movement.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/9
