OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1775754356
OL,3,CAlbert Bridge now closed to all
OL,4,Ctraffic, walkers and cyclists
OL,6,F"Our contractors are on site but the
OL,7,Fclosure will remain in place while we
OL,8,Fcontinue to monitor the bridge's
OL,9,Fmovements over the next 24 hours. We
OL,10,Fwill update when we know more," a
OL,11,Fstatement added.
OL,13,FPeople living nearby had mixed views
OL,14,Fabout the closure.
OL,16,F"It's very disruptive, very annoying,"
OL,17,Fsaid one cyclist trying to get to work.
OL,19,FA tourist described it as "ridiculous"
OL,20,Fand "overkill".
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
