FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1775754356
OL,3,CAlbert Bridge now closed to all
OL,4,Ctraffic, walkers and cyclists
OL,6,FBut some residents said the work had
OL,7,Fto be done and the council should be
OL,8,Fallowed to get on with the maintenance
OL,9,Fas quickly as possible.
OL,11,FAlbert Bridge is normally used by
OL,12,F20,000 cars each day and serves as a
OL,13,Fkey route for residents and businesses.
OL,15,FTimeline of London's Albert Bridge
OL,17,F1873 - OpeningAlbert Bridge, designed
OL,18,Fby Rowland Mason Ordish and named
OL,19,Fafter Prince Albert, opens as a hybrid
OL,20,Fsuspension and cable-stayed bridge
OL,21,Flinking Chelsea and Battersea.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/9
