OL,3,CAlbert Bridge now closed to all
OL,4,Ctraffic, walkers and cyclists
OL,6,F1884 - Early strengtheningCast-iron
OL,7,Fpiles are added to improve stability
OL,8,Funder increasing traffic.
OL,10,FEarly 20th century - Ongoing
OL,11,FmaintenanceRoutine repairs continue as
OL,12,Fthe narrow Victorian bridge adapts to
OL,13,Fheavier vehicles.
OL,15,F1973-1975 - Major
OL,16,FreinforcementExtensive structural
OL,17,Fworks on the piers and deck preserve
OL,18,Fthe bridge for continued use.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/9
