OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1775754356
OL,3,CAlbert Bridge now closed to all
OL,4,Ctraffic, walkers and cyclists
OL,6,F1970s - Weight restrictions
OL,7,FintroducedA three-tonne limit is
OL,8,Fimposed to protect the fragile
OL,9,Fstructure - pedestrians and cyclists
OL,10,Fbecome the primary users.
OL,12,FLate 20th century - Cultural
OL,13,FsignificanceThe bridge gains iconic
OL,14,Fstatus with its pastel Victorian
OL,15,Fpaintwork and scenic riverside views.
OL,17,F2010s - Preservation and minor
OL,18,FrepairsRoutine maintenance continues,
OL,19,Fensuring the bridge remains safe for
OL,20,Flight traffic and pedestrian use.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
