PN,40206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1775754356
OL,3,CAlbert Bridge now closed to all
OL,4,Ctraffic, walkers and cyclists
OL,6,F2024 - Weight limit enforcement
OL,7,FstrengthenedCameras begin issuing
OL,8,Ffines to vehicles exceeding three
OL,9,Ftonnes to protect the historic
OL,10,Fstructure.
OL,12,FFebruary 2026 - Precautionary closure
OL,13,Fto vehiclesKensington and Chelsea
OL,14,FCouncil closes the bridge to motor
OL,15,Ftraffic following a structural
OL,16,Finspection. Pedestrians and cyclists
OL,17,Fcan still cross, while cars are
OL,18,Fdiverted via Chelsea and Battersea
OL,19,Fbridges.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/9
