PN,40207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1775754356
OL,3,CAlbert Bridge now closed to all
OL,4,Ctraffic, walkers and cyclists
OL,6,FThe council will be keen to avoid a
OL,7,Frepeat of the long-term controversial
OL,8,Fclosure of Hammersmith Bridge which is
OL,9,Fonly open to pedestrians and cyclists.
OL,11,FThe crossing over the River Thames in
OL,12,Fwest London has been closed to motor
OL,13,Fvehicles since April 2019 after a
OL,14,Fsafety assessment uncovered dangerous
OL,15,Fmicrofractures in the castiron
OL,16,Fpedestals.
OL,18,FThe fractures made the crossing unsafe
OL,19,Ffor cars, buses and heavy traffic.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/9
